<:role: ROM Distilled — Phase C v3 欠陥修正と実験パイプライン確定 {#sec_01_main} :>

<:data search_index:
  keywords: Phase_C, v3, defect_fix, structural_isomer, ccl_edit_dist, MAX_LEN, R@k, ablation, diagnostic, CodeLlama, QLoRA
